A Saudi citizen, '''Fahad al-Shehri''' was deported from Canada in 1997 on charges he had engaged in terrorism.<ref>Bell, Stewart. "Cold Terror", 2005</ref>

He was a known associate of [[Mohamed Harkat]], a Canadian accused of links to the Algerian [[Groupe Islamique Armé]].<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/cdnsecurity/harkat.html "The CSIS case against Mohamed Harkat"], ''[[CBC News]]'', Toronto, July 17, 2006. Retrieved on 6 November 2016.</ref>
