The following is a list of a notable people who have at one time been known to {{Nihongo|[[cosplay]]|コスプレ|kosupure}}. Short for "costume play", it is an activity in which participants wear [[costume]]s and [[Fashion accessory|accessories]] to represent a specific [[Character (arts)|character]] or idea from a work of fiction.

